{cite web|url=http://www.pcpro.co.uk/blogs/2009/10/14/acer-3d-laptop-review-first-look/|title=Acer 3D laptop review: first look|publisher=}}</ref> 3D laptop, which includes Dynamic Digital Depth TriDef software.<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.engadget.com/2009/10/21/acers-3d-equipped-aspire-5738dg-laptop-gets-official-examined/|title=Acer's 3D-equipped Aspire 5738DG laptop gets official, examined|last=Melanson|first=Donald|publisher=Engadget}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.theregister.co.uk/2009/10/28/ddd_acer_3d_laptop/|title=Hands on with Acer's 3D laptop|last2=tweet_btn()|first2=James Sherwood|publisher=|first1=28 Oct 2009 at|last1=10:23}}</ref>\n\nThe Acer Aspire 5738PG computer also includes the Acer [[multi-touch]] technology.<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://us.acer.com/showrooms/touch/touchscreen.html|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20100111031106/http://us.acer.com/showrooms/touch/touchscreen.html|url-status=dead|title=Acer Official Site: Technology - Acer Touch<!-- Bot generated title -->|archivedate=January 11, 2010}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.pcworld.idg.com.au/slideshow/318267/acer-launches-new-touch-screen-monitor-notebooks/|title=Acer launches new touch-screen monitor, notebooks|publisher=}}</ref>\n\n{{Clear}}\n\n==References==\n\n{{reflist}}\n\n==External links==\n* [http://www.acer.com/ Acer Official Website]\n\n{{Acer Inc.}}\n\n[[Category:Acer products]]\n[[Category:Personal computers]]\n[[Category:Laptops]]\n[[Category:Acer laptops]]\n[[Category:Consumer electronics brands]]\n", "name_user": "Bhashu223", "label": "safe", "comment": "New product launched in 2020 aspire new modal", "url_page": "//en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Acer_Aspire_laptops"}
